parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to replace the defective Takata airbag inflators can cause serious or fatal injuries in the event of a crash, as the inflators may rupture during deployment.
symptoms: as the issue is related to a potential failure of the airbag system in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power rear cargo door can cause serious injury or even death due to its large size and heavy weight, which can come down quickly and without warning, striking individuals behind the vehicle.
symptoms: The power rear cargo door closes suddenly without warning
fails to retract when hitting an obstacle
and can cause injury or damage to individuals or property.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can cause difficulty or impossibility in exiting the vehicle, especially in emergency situations, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: and the exterior door handle falls off
making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended unlocking of the rear lift door access can cause the door to open while driving, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The rear lift door access unlocks on its own frequently
and the whole rear door lifts open while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Black Chrome Paint on Window Frames Peeling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the black chrome paint on window frames can cause aesthetic issues and potentially lead to rust or corrosion.
symptoms: The black chrome paint on window frames peels away.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Heated Seat Module and Wiring Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heated seat module and wiring can cause a fire hazard, potentially leading to vehicle damage or personal injury.
symptoms: visible damage to the wiring and connectors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unstable brake performance can cause loss of control, accidents, or injuries, especially when stopping at lights or stop signs.
symptoms: Vehicle feels like it slips before the brakes kick in
similar to the recall issue on 2015-2017 models.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power outlet can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to electrical system damage.
